      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! I've absolutely babied this car\u2014always kept it in the garage and made sure it stayed spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. I\u2019m looking for a quick sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move. Come check it out, you\u2019re going to love it!",
