    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for exceptional volumetric efficiency. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable Differential Lock, providing unparalleled mechanical feedback. This specimen is structurally pristine; the rear subframe mounting points are fatigue-free, and the factory suspension geometry remains unaltered. Meticulously maintained, the vehicle has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and VANOS overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain operates with surgical precision. The exterior retains its factory depth, while the interior displays zero bolster wear, making this one of the finest surviving examples of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated pinnacle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
