    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car, with no leaks, no rattles, and a spotless undercarriage. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
